osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千祈唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff9d3428a1c6a3a319a0163d5d23ba9ea5d4b6f","tid":1659382,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c5a91026293f795ee1c3c925f75c41da3b8e818","tid":1659382,"uid":309873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"P牌投唔到！<br />\n唔好搞南亞香港人呀！佢地都係香港人呀！<br />\n<br />\n幾個南亞人出手你就搞全部南亞，咁有純正廣東話廢老搞示威者駛唔駛殺晒華人？繼續渣佢春袋畀經濟壓力黨鐵嗰啲好過！"},{"pid":"fc41c88d2d5d7778f436da42408150f6f0db1546","tid":1659382,"uid":320154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:26:54.000Z","msg":"投唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絕不搞任何南亞裔居民/建築物<br />\n佢地都係收錢做嘢，即係有人係背後比好多錢搞<br />\n唔排除係黑狗高層做，一係鄉黑"},{"pid":"53cbc73a189c9548d1f8b016ace550196c957122","tid":1659382,"uid":120945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕不搞任何南亞裔居民/建築物"},{"pid":"2815da9f6fe0329d742536971b9251f254b4d93a","tid":1659382,"uid":81800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:27:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a3076f0208dead6a02c84ddb0115cdc0c7ac3ce","tid":1659382,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:27:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adc395c81fccecf2c5b1a8da3e7af630b8cb74e3","tid":1659382,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> IG &ldquo;bye bye starbucks&rdquo; challenge</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659200</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦各位， 比美心負皮緊呀。"},{"pid":"30f773cfe7177a672be14dbb0006a7effb98dbc2","tid":1659382,"uid":44673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-